
'''= community-owned data commons for biodiversity: "GainForest.Earth is a decentralized science non-profit archiving earth’s nature data to inform transparent environmental decision making".'''

URL = https://gainforest.earth/


=Description=

"Only 1% of global biodiversity data comes from the
world's largest rainforests. We're changing this by
turning local communities into Indigenous scientists
and help organisations build equitable data products
that can preserve nature.

We are pioneering decentralized data collection
as a sustainable income source for communities.
Our community-elected GainForest Data Council
sets the current prices for data."

(https://gainforest.earth/)


